Package io.straas.android.sdk.circall.exception

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CircallException  
    PrepareException  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CircallException.CameraSwitchErrorException
    Camera switch error, maybe permission problem or other camera problems.
    CircallException.CancelledException
    Current task is cancelled by developer.
    CircallException.InternalException
    Internal error occurs.
    CircallException.InterruptedException
    Current task is interrupted by developer.
    CircallException.InvalidTokenException
    The CirCall token is invalid, maybe it's wrong or expired.
    CircallException.InvalidVideoFrameException
    The CircallStream to capture snapshot is invalid, maybe video CircallStream or CircallPlayerView is invalid or not ready.
    CircallException.NetworkException
    Couldn't connect to server.
    CircallException.PermissionDeniedException
    This task is not permitted by server since what you want to do is not allowed here.
    CircallException.PublishStreamException
    Called when a streaming error occurs in local CircallStream, maybe local streaming data path is lost or streaming connection is disconnected suddenly.
    CircallException.RequestRejectedException
    This occurs when developer is trying to invoke a method with wrong parameter causing IllegalArgumentException or calling a method in wrong state causing IllegalStateException.
    CircallException.ServerException
    An error occurs on server side.
    CircallException.SubscribeStreamException
    Called when a streaming error occurs in remote CircallStream, maybe remote streaming data path is lost or streaming connection is disconnected suddenly.
    CircallException.UnauthorizedException
    The user is unauthorized.
    CircallException.UnexpectedCircallApiResponse
    Received unexpected CirCall API response.
    PrepareException.CameraInitFailException
    Camera initialization fails, maybe permission problem or other camera problems.
    PrepareException.MicrophoneInitFailException
    Microphone initialization fails, maybe permission problem or other microphone problems.
    PrepareException.RequestRejectedException
    This occurs when developer is trying calling a method in wrong state causing IllegalStateException.
